code packages:
Parent Package	Sub-Package	Description
config	AuthenticationHandler	Manages authentication and authorization logic.
	SecurityConfig	Configures security settings, such as access control and encryption.
utils	CommonFuncs	Contains general utility functions used across the application.
	SecurityUtils	Provides security-related utilities, such as hashing and token validation.
controller	GuestController	Handles guest-related operations, such as viewing programs and test schedules.
	StudentController	Manages student operations, such as registration and application submission.
	LogStaffController	Handles logistics staff interactions, such as managing test venues.
	AdmStaffController	Manages admission staff tasks, such as reviewing applications.
	ExternalController	Bridges external services and APIs with the system.
	InternalController	Manages internal system interactions and service coordination.
ExternalController	DocVerifier	Verifies uploaded documents, such as transcripts and certificates.
	CertVerifier	Validates student certificates using external sources.
repository	DatabaseRepo	Provides database access for various entities.
	StorageRepo	Manages interactions with cloud storage, such as S3.
entity	User	Represents student and staff user accounts.
	Test	Stores test-related information, such as schedule and results.
	Venue	Defines venue details for exams and interviews.
	Interview	Stores interview-related details.
	Payment	Represents payment transactions and statuses.
	Form	Manages application forms and submitted documents.
	UserDetail	Stores additional user information, such as contact details.
	Program	Defines the academic programs available for application.
InternalController	DatabaseService	Handles database operations and queries.
	StorageService	Manages file storage and retrieval operations.
	EmailService	Sends notifications and confirmation emails.
	PaymentService	Handles payment processing and transaction verification.

screens:
Category	Requirement
Phone Verification	Users enter and verify their phone number to proceed with registration.
Email Verification	Users verify their email address via a confirmation link.
Registration	New users fill out their details to create an account.
Login	Users enter credentials to access the system.
Reset Password	Users reset their password via email verification.
Home Page	The main dashboard where users access all features.
Application Status	Users check their application progress and updates.
Contact Support	Users can request help or ask questions.
Personal Information	Users enter and update their personal details.
Admission Requirements	Displays information on eligibility and necessary documents.
Program Overview	Users browse available programs and their details.
Program Selection	Users select their desired programs for application.
Application Form	Users fill out and submit the admission application.
FPT DNG / FPT Pay	External payment gateway integration for fee submission.
Enrollment Confirmation	Users confirm their enrollment and submit necessary documents.
Venue Detail	Displays test/interview venue details for applicants.
Staff Dashboard	Admissions staff manage applications, interviews, and tests.
Application Detail	Staff review individual application information.
Application Status (Staff)	Admissions staff track application statuses.
Certificate Verification	Staff verify submitted certificates and academic records.
Document Verification	Staff review and verify user-uploaded documents.
Assign Interview	Staff schedule interview sessions for applicants.
Assign Test	Staff schedule entrance tests for applicants.
Assign Venue & Time	Staff assign applicants to test/interview venues and times.
Test List	Staff view a list of scheduled tests.
Test Detail	Staff access details of specific tests.
Interview List	Staff view a list of scheduled interviews.